OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774605947
OL,3,CSir Paul McCartney releases new single
OL,4,Cand announces first album for five
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FSir Paul McCartney has announced his
OL,8,Ffirst album in five years - releasing
OL,9,Fthe first single from it.
OL,11,FThe introspective 14-track record,
OL,12,Ftitled The Boys Of Dungeon Lane,
OL,13,Frecounts a collection of memories from
OL,14,Fthe singer's formative years in
OL,15,FLiverpool including his early
OL,16,Fadventures with his late bandmates
OL,17,FGeorge Harrison and John Lennon, prior
OL,18,Fto their Beatles fame.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
