PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774605947
OL,3,CSir Paul McCartney releases new single
OL,4,Cand announces first album for five
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FSir Paul named the album after Dungeon
OL,8,FLane, a place close to his childhood
OL,9,Fhome in Forthlin Road in the Liverpool
OL,10,Fsuburb of Speke.
OL,12,FIt is referenced in the newly released
OL,13,Ftrack Days We Left Behind, which Sir
OL,14,FPaul described as a "memory song" that
OL,15,Finspired the album title.
OL,17,FSir Paul said: "I was thinking just
OL,18,Fthat, about the days I left behind and
OL,19,FI do often wonder if I'm just writing
OL,20,Fabout the past but then I think, how
OL,21,Fcan you write about anything else?
OL,26,@vD@UOUvD@aO]yD@POU
