PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774605947
OL,3,CSir Paul McCartney releases new single
OL,4,Cand announces first album for five
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,F"It's just a lot of memories of
OL,8,FLiverpool.
OL,10,F"We didn't have much at all but it
OL,11,Fdidn't matter because all the people
OL,12,Fwere great and you didn't notice you
OL,13,Fdidn't have much."
OL,15,FThe record will also feature a number
OL,16,Fof new love songs and reflections from
OL,17,Fthe artist on his life before he found
OL,18,Fglobal fame.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUuD@RO]
