OL,3,CSir Paul McCartney releases new single
OL,4,Cand announces first album for five
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FSir Paul's new studio album was
OL,8,Fproduced by Andrew Watt and began
OL,9,Fnearly five years ago with the opening
OL,10,Ftrack, As You Lie There.
OL,12,FThe Beatles was formed in 1960 and
OL,13,Fmade up of Sir Paul, Lennon, Harrison
OL,14,Fand Sir Ringo Starr.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
