PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774605947
OL,3,CSir Paul McCartney releases new single
OL,4,Cand announces first album for five
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FThe group becoming the best-selling
OL,8,Fmusical act of all time and one of the
OL,9,Fmost influential groups in the world,
OL,10,Fhaving achieved 16 UK number one
OL,11,Falbums and 18 UK number one singles
OL,12,Fincluding Help!, Hey Jude and She
OL,13,FLoves You.
OL,15,FFollowing their split in 1970, Sir
OL,16,FPaul released his debut solo album,
OL,17,FMcCartney.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
