PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774605947
OL,3,CSir Paul McCartney releases new single
OL,4,Cand announces first album for five
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FHe also formed the band Wings with his
OL,8,Flate wife Linda McCartney along with
OL,9,Fformer Moody Blues guitarist Denny
OL,10,FLaine.
OL,12,FPrior to splitting in 1981, the band
OL,13,Frecorded seven studio albums including
OL,14,FBand On The Run and achieved 12 UK top
OL,15,F10 singles including Jet, Silly Love
OL,16,FSongs and Live And Let Die, the theme
OL,17,Fto the 1973 James Bond film.
OL,19,FSir Paul McCartney's new album The
OL,20,FBoys Of Dungeon Lane will be out on 29
OL,21,FMay.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
